cated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":227,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" level. Need to verify\",\"session_id\":\"a3680f7e-0b6d-44a0-bebb-f72e7a9829f8\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784768421}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":242,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-b253af3b-5cab-47a2-a278-e7044b561bfc-37\\nfc_30a2314b-1dd5-9557-9ca0-31cb1b2b21cd_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"utils/server|Host|engine\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md\",\"glob\":\"*.md\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-b253af3b-5cab-47a2-a278-e7044b561bfc-37\\nfc_30a2314b-1dd5-9557-9ca0-31cb1b2b21cd_1\",\"offset\":0},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"utils/server|Host|engine\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md\",\"outputMode\":\"content\",\"workspaceResults\":{\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\":{\"content\":{\"matches\":[{\"file\":\"docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":30,\"content\":\"  engineIOModule/   # Server-only：本机引擎 Port IO（禁止 Client 引用）\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":358,\"content\": [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":243,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-b253af3b-5cab-47a2-a278-e7044b561bfc-38\\nfc_30a2314b-1dd5-9557-9ca0-31cb1b2b21cd_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":120},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# Studio V2 前端目录结构与落点规则\\n\\n> 本文是 Studio V2 前端目录结构的真源。  \\n> 目的不是追求抽象优雅，而是让人类、Cursor、批执行器和门禁脚本都能一眼判断：一个文件应该放在哪里，不应该放在哪里。\\n\\n## 1. 为什么需要这份规则\\n\\nStudio V2 第一阶段是静态页重构，不要求真实保存、真实调试或真实导入导出闭环。\\n\\n但静态阶段也必须保证代码地基不歪。如果目录边界不清晰，AI 会自然出现以下退化：\\n\\n- 先平铺文件，再为了过门禁移动到子目录。\\n- 移动后保留兼容转发文件，导致父目录和子目录长期并存。\\n- `features`、`domain`、`services` 被不同执行者解释成不同含义。\\n- 页面组件、业务编排、mock 数据、类型契约混在一起。\\n- 后续真实功能接入时，只能在已经歪掉的结构上继续堆。\\n\\n因此 Studio V2 从此只认固定目录结构。任何新增、迁移、修复任务都必须先判断目标文件属于哪一类，再落到对应目录。\\n\\n## 2. 顶层结构\\n\\nStudio V2 前端只认以下顶层业务目录：\\n\\n```text\\napps/studioV2/\\n  app/\\n  src/\\n  typeFiles/\\n  tests/\\n  engineIOModule/   # Server-only：本机引擎 Port IO（禁止 Client 引用）\\n```\\n\\n其它顶层业务目录默认禁止。\\n\\n允许的工程目录包括： [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":273,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-6dc6b81c-3a8e-4514-8899-8ab582959923-46\\nfc_556fc1f5-7dba-9905-8289-578ab6c035db_5\",\"tool_call\":{\"updateTodosToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"todos\":[{\"id\":\"read-docs\",\"content\":\"读必读文档与 V2-IO-9 任务定义\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_COMPLETED\",\"createdAt\":\"1784784722260\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784784772363\",\"dependencies\":[]},{\"id\":\"impl-v2-io-9\",\"content\":\"实现 V2-IO-9（仅此任务）\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_IN_PROGRESS\",\"createdAt\":\"1784784722260\",\"updatedAt\":\"1784784772363\",\"dependencies\":[]}],\"merge\":true}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-6dc6b81c-3a8e-4514-8899-8ab582959923-46\\nfc_556fc1f5-7dba-9905-8289-578ab6c035db_5\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784784772363\"},\"model_call_id\":\"51f4eeec-4abc-4338-82b6-7ffa26490294-9-cajq\",\"session_id\":\"a3680f7e-0b6d-44a0-bebb-f72e7a9829f8\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784772325}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":275,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-6dc6b81c-3a8e-4514-8899-8ab582959923-46\\nfc_556fc1f5-7dba-9905-8289-578ab6c035db_5\",\"tool_call\":{\"updateTodosToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"todos\":[{\"id\":\"read-docs\",\"content\":\"读必读文档与 V2-IO-9 任务定义\",\"status\":\"TODO_STATUS_COMPLETED\",\"cr